{"tid":1365923,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"「月經」究竟依家係政府工好定係大型私人公司好？1","createTime":"2019-07-25T20:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T06:23:38.000Z","uid":216555,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b2c0278f5beb364680d32bddb519a9fe4ed04420","tid":1365923,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T20:06:55.000Z","msg":"政府工依家冇咗長俸 年假少咗 冇醫療 <br />\n用兩電一鐵作為例子 <br />\n三間大公司都有人壽保險醫療 <br />\n最少13 個月<br />\n電費津貼咁cheap就唔講la <br />\n而家中電去到某個職位有免息供樓<br />\n中電推出多個「家庭及社會友善」假期福利，包括5天婚假、16周分娩假、10日侍產假、以及今年新增的10日領養假<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNNT6Kq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNNT6Kq.png&h=7947408c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港燈</span> 據我所知好似仲行緊公積金<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6eP7rK5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6eP7rK5.png&h=36974b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n究竟而家嘅風向係大公司是定係政府工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梗係政府工啦傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n梗係私人公司啦柒碌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cefdb305bf2ba79829d7c9e71b73825b0157987","tid":1365923,"uid":27266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T20:20:57.000Z","msg":"大公司&gt;正苦&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;SME"},{"pid":"5edfa64c67b3ac48106653b10017e9208bb5298d","tid":1365923,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:32:53.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"9745789495bd7751051e8b52974bdde97286eed3","tid":1365923,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:20:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7bc7a65e2be4cbb05a997778655d55fbf8adc106","tid":1365923,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:21:11.000Z","msg":"政府18%mpf"},{"pid":"6f0a249dd44831ae1ecbecd16ea9a8cc737f0052","tid":1365923,"uid":33643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedB